<br>
Fantasy &quot;Paladins, Warriors, SK's are 'MT classes' and both cannot function together in a group&quot;.<br>
<br>
Reality &quot;All tank classes also do melee damage and sometimes other things.  Each brings a unique role to the group, and each contibutes more than simply tanking, and having more than one is acceptible and common practice.&quot;<br>
