I don't spend all my time tanking, especially at raids.  I do group with other tanks and when I do they generally are MT, Paladins do have value outside of tanking.  However you really are failing to realize just how low DPS most paladins are and just how weak our heals are at 65 in PoP.  If I can't fit into a group in the tanking slot, I'm more of a burden than a boon in general... unless its a odds and ends group that needs the backup healing a lot.  Again just because you disagree doesn't mean I'm some clueless moron.<br>
<br>
