jority of us warriors who are more casual gamers will never see.  Take a look at the mid level game, where, in similar gear, hybrids are just plain better in most situations, and certainly in xp groups. Not to mention soloing, which is pretty much not an option past 40 for warriors because of the risk and the downtime. Currently I'm 51st level, so I havent really seen the high end game yet, but I can say with certainty that from about 30 to 51, hybrids, particularly pallys and sk's outshine the warrior in most situations. And even at that level, what they lack in pure tanking ability they more than make up for with better ability to gain/keep aggro, better utility, and the ability to solo something that actually gives them xps.  <br>
